# Oneiroi firmware changelog

## 0.9.80 (2024-04-13)

- fixed random mode calibration
- calibration of pitch and looper speed center positions (<https://github.com/Befaco/Oneiroi/issues/17>)

## 0.9.79 (2024-04-10)

- allow calibrating without the need to erase patch and storage (<https://github.com/Befaco/Oneiroi/issues/19>)
- using C2, C5 and C8 as the three calibration points (<https://github.com/Befaco/Oneiroi/issues/17>)
- disabled USB audio (<https://github.com/Befaco/Oneiroi/issues/20>)
- using correct firmware version in device.h (<https://github.com/Befaco/Oneiroi/issues/32>)

## 0.9.78 (2024-04-05)

- fixed problems with CV's (<https://github.com/Befaco/Oneiroi/issues/22>)

## 0.9.77 (2024-04-04)

- three points v/oct calibration (<https://github.com/Befaco/Oneiroi/issues/17>)

## 0.9.76 (2024-03-31)

- changed both pre/post switch and record button to GPIO_INPUT (were EXTI), also
  fixing <https://github.com/Befaco/Oneiroi/issues/12>

## 0.9.75 (2024-03-29)

- fixed noisy faders with sine waves (<https://github.com/Befaco/Oneiroi/issues/13>)

## 0.9.74 (2024-03-24)

- fixed saving to flash

## 0.9.73

- reactivated bootloader
- README
